      "content": "Thanks for clarifying that. It sounds pretty risky if there's no cap. \n\nLooking back at the text, it says I have to hold them harmless from \"any and all losses... of whatever kind.\" That sounds incredibly broad. Are there any common ways people try to narrow this down, or is there something else in this specific wording that I should be particularly wary of?",
